&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of basic arithmetic including the ability to add, subtract, multiply, and divide&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to maintain confidentiality&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to promptly respond to issues and escalate them to the appropriate party&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to adapt and work in a fast-paced/dynamic environment&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to communicate effectively with team members and supervisors&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to closely follow instructions/process&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrate teamwork as well as the ability to work independently&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong attention to detail, including the ability to produce accurate and consistent data&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
